{
  "stem": "16571.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On a local train [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with a transport of women to-- it finished up-- later I realized it was another camp called Belsen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was still in civilian clothes, dressed like a toff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it-- a woman transport arrived at the same time, all looking very hungry, almost starving.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the officer went up and reported special transport, what I took it to be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the guy at the gate said, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let them go in with the rest of them, with the women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, special transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Special delivery.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were taken to a block-- was a ladies'-- a woman's block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they started with the young-- young-- younger ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They put them in tubs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these ladies, Jewish women, they were scrubbing and washing them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First time I've seen soap since I left home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was sort of starting being a little embarrassed because there was these women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after all, I was now 15 and 1/2 or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was sort of thinking about, you know, they going to wash me and all the rest of it, my private parts.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But before-- I needn't have worried-- before the last four or five were taken to be scrubbed and washed, a German came.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He called out our numbers, and he took us off to another part of the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't-- and-- and for 30 years or more, I was thinking, what was the idea behind it?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why, why, why, why, why?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I spoke to a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a nurse-- a-- a sister, in fact, she-- she is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was telling her this very same story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And suddenly, she woke me up and said, don't you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
